highlights.title: Problem Solver
highlights.description: Passionate about using data to solve complex business problems and improve decision-making processes.

highlights.title: Critical Thinker
highlights.description: Evaluate information objectively, identify patterns and anomalies, and draw well-reasoned conclusions from diverse data sources.

highlights.title: Data Storytelling
highlights.description: Bridge the gap between data and decision-making by creating compelling stories that reveal insights and drive business outcomes.

highlights.title: Time Management
highlights.description: Efficiently balance multiple data projects and deadlines while maintaining high-quality analytical standards and meeting critical business timelines.
